---
title: Swedish Pork Meatballs & Creamy Bacon Sauce with Garlicky Greens & Cheesy Mash
description: With two kinds of proteins: juicy pork and crispy bacon in the creamy sauce, these Swedish-style meatballs are pure comfort food. Add a cheesy mash, with tart cherry sauce and greens and you'll have a dish paying homage to the true Scandi spirit.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/655462704c741be7da5ddac1-141143df.jpeg
